    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Strings which guide and support children who are learning to walk.  Sometimes in the form of reinforced cloth attached to the shoulders and hanging to the ankles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
